vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) a joint election agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas, Dallas County, and various other jurisdictions within Dallas County, for the conduct of a joint election to be held on Saturday, May 3, 2025, in an amount not to exceed $1,033,010.75; (2) legal advertising in connection with the Saturday, May 3, 2025 General Election, in an amount not to exceed $150,000.00; and (3) $300.00 for translation services for publication and posting notices related to the election - Not to exceed $1,183,310.75 - Financing: General Fund
